Instructions to push/pull to/from multiple repositories.

The vmware repositories are internal so I cant pull from a remote location.

The only way is to push from my mac to two repositories at once.

To do so one can have multiple repositories added as such:

git remote add gitlab <gitlab_repository_url>
git remote add github <github_repository_url>


and then to check:

git remote -v

And the nto push :
git add <file> 
git commit -m "reason"
git push gitlab
git push github



